description: In this episode, Lisa, Jamie, and Mikey tried 15 food finds!!! What did they try? A killer butternut squash sauce, yummy lemongrass chicken, avocado ice cream, instant boba packs, an incredible dip from Tribe, cauliflower linguine, and so much more! Plus, the most interesting find of them all: shelf stable sausage that is OUT OF THIS WORLD! You must push play right now, then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of all the products mentioned in the episode!
